Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华 你收到过邮局送来的信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是电子邮件哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…不多呢 也就是派对的邀请函吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 也就只有那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说电子邮件也很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.89,0:00:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是实体的信好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如不幸之信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是决斗书
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.32,0:00:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那些吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 新威尼斯快要进入春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连太阳公公也一天一天地…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得暖洋洋的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是白天 也会困意连连…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重啊…亚利亚社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:00:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉地就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.63,0:01:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长 谢谢你叫醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮递员老伯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了啊 白天打盹很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…邮递员老伯看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我从下面看到你在打盹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.03,0:01:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得叫醒你就太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.94,0:01:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天呀 我是以顾客的身份来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.34,0:01:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实呢 老伯我的凤尾舟破了个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约需要一整天来修理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢 我想明天把你们的船包下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.92,0:01:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来收发邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.53,0:01:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我马上就去问一下艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:36.98,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那颗 新威尼斯色的心…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天跟我预约的客人实在太多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 小姑娘你来做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 灯里还是见习领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:04:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有指导人员在场 是没办法让客人乘坐的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的工作能不能找别人代替呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮局的人都说这是个好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆就休息一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这个与其说是工作 不如说是老伯我的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢 我舍不得休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行的话 就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊 委托这么奇怪的工作给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔除了自主练习之外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再请一些不同的人来指导怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说 邮递员先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是作为指导人员来指导我练习的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 这样小姑娘既能练习
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而老伯我也能收发邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一举两得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 社长先生也要一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,康纳瑞桥邮政局
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里了 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是今天来给邮递员老伯帮忙的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮递员老伯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 好像大家都是邮递员呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 我还不知道老伯的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你就是长老经常提起的那个领航员小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长老？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请里面走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好宏伟的建筑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有墨水的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里是邮局啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 小姑娘 你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老伯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么早就让你来 真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一天请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里 彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长先生 今天跟老伯戴一样的帽子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 开始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是早操哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为老伯的工作是体力活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能有点不好意思啦 不过这也是个仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就陪我们做一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那么我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮递员老伯被称为长老呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也有年轻人管我叫老伯啦 老爹什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊 老伯我就是个邮递员老伯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 要开始工作了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 靠近点 靠近点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都是如此精准迅速啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 要不也来试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就试试那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对对对…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 放回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全放回原处了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 第一次能这样很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:09:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下来的慢慢来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖力工作过后肚子一定饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.03,0:10:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个煎蛋卷好好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再继续努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:10:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午还要配送信件哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:10:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 亚利亚社长？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 社长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要寄信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这封信 我希望能立刻送到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天已经过了收信的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最快也要等到明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不送出去的话就来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收信人住很远吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那直接放进邮箱不是更快吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 因为典礼已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典礼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚典礼？谁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:11:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这是给老师的祝贺信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新娘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面写了「恭贺新婚」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也写了「对不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师辞职之前 有一个合唱比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我没有参加
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛期间 我一直躲在音乐室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让老师伤透脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在欢送会那天 我甚至还说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「老师不在以后可就轻松了」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时第一次看到老师流泪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封信给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你送到教堂去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你也要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 当然没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是亚利亚公司的领航员 水无灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小空 真好听的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 赶快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我用逆划过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆划？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就这样一直前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我给你去送信啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你 绫乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你幸福 绫乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫乃老师 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有您的信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄信人是小空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 总是给你惹麻烦 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢送会的时候说了这么过分的话 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你说「很轻松」 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…我最喜欢老师你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到你就要离开 就觉得很寂寞…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法对你说「恭喜」 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 恭喜你结婚了 要幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮递员先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送信完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师很高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小空真正的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛从信的字里行间传到我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小空而言 那就是他的最高祝福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:17:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对那孩子来说 我是个好老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小空 谢谢你的信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会给你回信的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你 老师 要保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:18:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再见 小空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮递员伯伯 谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 剩下的信件也要赶紧送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一封信送完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新娘子好像很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小空也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮递员老伯不舍得休息的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像也有点明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是一份很有意义的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.71,0:19:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天转了一整天 我才发现到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新威尼斯有很多邮筒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为这里的人还是习惯于写信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意做这种麻烦的事 一点都不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢 这是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 如果太急了 心情就没法平静下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信这种东西 收到的时候会很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开的时候就像打开宝箱一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情会变得像孩子一样兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且里面是以书信的形式表现出的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄信人的心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据内容的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时就会变成自己的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成一辈子都能用手触碰到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做「心」的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够用手触碰的「心」…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 信件能跨越时空的界限
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把写信的人带到自己面前来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新威尼斯城也和信件有相似之处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为创造这座城市的人们的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时都能用双手触碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢这个特意做麻烦事的城市呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 小姑娘你已经染上新威尼斯的颜色了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.76,0:21:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 艾莉西亚前辈 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这是今早送来的写给灯里的信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是邮递员老伯寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致小姑娘：
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.03,0:22:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮递员老伯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和邮递员老伯说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信件会把写信的人带到眼前呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.99,0:22:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 那封信虽然很短
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.74,0:22:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但褪色的墨水字迹却令人感受到浓浓的暖意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面还有邮递员先生那淡淡的烟味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里姐姐 你又多了一样宝物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写信啊…说起来我还真的没写过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次试着写写看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样我也能接近新威尼斯的色彩了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份 雨天的精彩…\N那个 春日的发现…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:15.85,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}窓からそっと 朝陽がのびて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:28.83,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}まどろむまつ毛に こぼれてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:43.87,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}そよふく風 部屋へと招いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:56.68,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}木漏れ日に 君の寝顔 優しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:56.68,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an7}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:03:03.00,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつものありふれた朝だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:10.61,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}鮮やかに色づいてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:18.09,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}それは君と巡り合えた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:21.63,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:28.40,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}君と一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:15.85,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}晨曦悄然漫入窗际
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:28.83,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}洒落在 舒睡的睫毛间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:43.87,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}让轻拂的风吹入小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:56.68,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}枝叶间滑落的阳光 映衬你的睡颜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:56.68,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:03:03.00,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}虽是个平凡无奇的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:10.61,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}也染上了艳丽的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:18.09,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是与你邂逅的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:21.63,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}我并非孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:28.40,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}因为 有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:57.14,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}雨が上がる 遠く空眺め 雲の切れ間探す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.99,0:23:08.99,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつもよりも 少し遠回り 海へ続く道を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.65,0:23:16.72,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}切りすぎた前髪 気にしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:21.33,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}そのまま 駆け出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.16,0:23:28.21,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}頬をかすめていく 風の色が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:33.81,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつか夏のはじまりを告げる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:40.02,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}大きく手を振って 深呼吸しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.22,0:23:45.63,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}この時間を抱きしめていたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.83,0:23:50.77,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}明日もまた会えるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:57.14,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}雨过天晴 眺望遥远的天空 探寻云彩的缝隙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.99,0:23:08.99,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}绕过早已习惯的归途 向着通往大海的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.65,0:23:16.72,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}忘掉剪得过短的留海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:21.33,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}毫无顾忌地大胆前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.16,0:23:28.21,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}吹拂着面颊的海风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:33.81,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}不知何时染上了初夏的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:40.02,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}用力挥挥手 来个深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.22,0:23:45.63,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}满心希望永远拥抱这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.83,0:23:50.77,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}明天 我们还会再见吗


